# Normalize all text to LF in the repo and on checkout. The contract hashes
# working-tree files (e.g. SKILL.md), so a CRLF working tree silently diverges
# from the LF-committed content and breaks fixtures on a fresh clone.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary fixtures must be byte-stable across clones: never apply line-ending
# normalization, or raw-bytes SHA-256 subject bindings break on checkout.
*.bin binary
